{"tid":829890,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"卓林情侶檔Sell工作室：永不放棄","createTime":"2018-09-20T20:18:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-21T08:49:04.000Z","uid":130626,"like":2,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b0cf0262c6640c9e86aa7e1ebcf6f9df3da5363f","tid":829890,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T20:18:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/WlsvSZl1zoX_R1nnZcWDDA--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l/http://media.zenfs.com/en_us/News/singtao/20180920f180947.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FWlsvSZl1zoX_R1nnZcWDDA--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTAwO2g9NDAwO2lsPXBsYW5l%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen_us%2FNews%2Fsingtao%2F20180920f180947.jpg&h=a8bbbcb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n【星島日報報道】吳綺莉女兒吳卓林去年底跟同性伴侶Andi回家鄉加拿大生活，有網民不時在多倫多士嘉堡捕獲二人。今年初卓林與Andi拍片求助後，至本月初已開展新生活，開社交平台新帳號外，又共同開設工作室做生意。<br />\n<br />\n工作室的instagram上載卓林與Andi的合照，二人穿黑白Look情侶裝、染灰髮，以英文留言稱他們失去了一切，以夢想表達自我，透過工作室展示他們如何成長為一對愛侶，並分享以愛和野心去拯救生命的經驗。在另一個Post，二人又表示永不放棄：「Homeless to heaven；never give up」。"},{"pid":"858b8302f25461f00a48b6c4516b21e0dacb94ce","tid":829890,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T23:25:27.000Z","msg":"又想唔靠屋企<br />\n但又要靠老豆個名先有理<br />\n<br />\n好矛盾呀"},{"pid":"d4fb31fc52086b9230368448c4d6f0eaab052a77","tid":829890,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"858b8302f25461f00a48b6c4516b21e0dacb94ce","tid":829890,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T23:25:27.000Z","msg":"又想唔靠屋企<br />\n但又要靠老豆個名先有理<br />\n<br />\n好矛盾呀"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T08:44:09.000Z","msg":"明顯係扮哂野啦"},{"pid":"976b343be2ae96332f1ff375ea7f56dd93278851","tid":829890,"uid":31126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T08:49:04.000Z","msg":"死tb又病發"}]}